     SHORT="gweled is puzzle game."
      LONG="
gweled is a GNOME version of a popular game 
called Bejeweled or Diamond Mine.
The aim of the game is to make an alignment 
of 3 or more gems, either vertically or 
horizontally, by swapping adjacent gems.
The game ends when there are no possible moves left.
